msgstr "<refname>labplot</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"an application by KDE for interactive graphing and analysis of scientific "
"data."
msgstr ""
"een KDE-toepassing voor het interactief grafieken maken en het analyseren "
"van wetenschappelijke gegevens."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>LabPlot options</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>file</replaceable></arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>labplot</command> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>LabPlot-opties</"
"replaceable></arg> <arg choice=\"opt\"><replaceable>bestand</replaceable></"
"arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beschrijving"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot is a data plotting and analysis tool."
msgstr "LabPlot is een hulpmiddel voor het plotten en analyseren van gegevens."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Its features include 2D and 3D data and function plotting, easy editing of "
"plots, analysis of data and functions, support for different worksheets "
"using MDI and LabPlot project files."
msgstr ""
"Tot de mogelijkheden behoren het plotten van 2D- en 3D-functies, eenvoudige "
"plotbewerking, analyse van gegevens en functies, ondersteuning voor diverse "
"werkbladen met gebruik van MDI- en LabPlot-projectbestanden."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Note that LabPlot is called using <command>labplot</command>."
msgstr "Merk op dat LabPlot wordt aangeroepen met <command>labplot</command>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "LabPlot options"
msgstr "Opties voor LabPlot"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For a full summary of generic options, run <userinput><command>labplot</"
"command> <parameter>--help</parameter></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Een volledige samenvatting van de algemene opties krijgt u met "
"<userinput><command>labplot</command> <parameter>--help</parameter></"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "--no-splash"
msgstr "--no-splash"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not show the splash screen."
msgstr "Geen splash-screen tonen."

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "--presenter"
msgstr "--presenter"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start in the presenter mode."
msgstr "In presentatiemodus starten"

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arguments"
msgstr "Argumenten"

#. Tag: option
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "file"
msgstr "bestand"

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location of the project to be opened, usually ending with <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml</literal>."
msgstr ""
"De locatie van het te openen project, gewoonlijk eindigend op <literal role="
"\"extension\">.lml</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The project file can be also compressed, with its filename ending with "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">."
"lml.bz2</literal> or <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.xz</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Het projectbestand kan ook zijn ingepakt, de bestandsnaam eindigt dan op "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.lml.gz</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">."
"lml.bz2</literal> of <literal role=\"extension\">.lml.xz</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Zie ook"

#. Tag: member
#: man-labplot.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full user documentation is available through the KDE Help Centre. You can "
"also enter the URL <ulink url=\"help:/labplot\">help:/labplot</ulink> "
"(either enter this <acronym>URL</acronym> into &dolphin;, or run "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/labplot</"
"parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Een volledige gebruikersdocumentatie vindt u in de KDE Help Centre. U kunt "
"ook de URL <ulink url=\"help:/labplot\">help:/labplot</ulink> invoeren (of "
"ook <acronym>URL</acronym> into &dolphin;, of  "
"<userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> <parameter>help:/labplot</"
"parameter></userinput>)."

